/>\n因為男人臉岩蠶，臉形唔順滑。<br />\n披個長髮落去會令塊臉既凹突位更突岀，睇落去好陰深。而且五官同圓形既外圍（長髮包住個頭）唔和諧。<br />\n所以男人都可以長，要電到有d力唔好貼住塊面is ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:42:01.000Z","msg":"披短散髮係無禮貌，古代髮型要配合身份，有唔同綁法。唔同綁法可以解決面形問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"更正*披頭散髮<br />\n<br />\n法國時裝代表路易十四係戴假長髮。古埃及有史料記載戴假髮目的係美觀及身份。藝術家達文西畫既男人無邊個係短毛，包括自畫。耶穌作為文藝復興極重要既model，係以夏韶聲髮型示人。我相信耶穌畫像好明顥受到歐化，同現代猶太人都有返咁上下距離，應該就係為咗美而選擇失真。<br />\n<br />\n華夏把頭髮視作身體一部分，保養身體(包括頭髮) 係孝既一種體現。孝經:身體髮膚，受之父母，不敢毀傷，孝之始也。當然華夏文明既出發點同「美」係無乜關係，因為般都唔會強調男人同美有關係，但成個文明無邊段時間係短髮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://x0.ifengimg.com/ucms/2020_14/C39658221BDB65EE14CFD68C373B3B18F67561B8_w640_h426.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx0.ifengimg.com%2Fucms%2F2020_14%2FC39658221BDB65EE14CFD68C373B3B18F67561B8_w640_h426.png&h=c185788e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文藝復興三傑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5f/Louis_XIV_of_France.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F5%2F5f%2FLouis_XIV_of_France.jpg&h=23d3056e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路易十四<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.discoverwalks.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/the-last-supper-restored-da-vinci_32x16-1536x768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoverwalks.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fthe-last-supper-restored-da-vinci_32x16-1536x768.jpg&h=781cf7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後晚餐，一半人都係長過膊頭，包括耶穌。"},{"pid":"6fed9f7428f834f2dfef7922d933d05c25217a20","tid":2379554,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"404e4ae2234117db43dc858b644bc014af2b9aba","tid":2379554,"uid":232575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9d7e376574bb4d7130fa90a430c097f84a24c95","tid":2379554,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec06a8b7ad002615524bfaa94a7e4d21ca9c958","tid":2379554,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"202